                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 mb-16">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-cyan-400/20 h-full">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What is Ocean Albedo?</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                                Albedo refers to the fraction of sunlight that is reflected by a surface. Ocean albedo varies based on factors like:
                            </p>
                            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 mb-6">
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i data-feather="check-circle" class="text-cyan-400 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span>Solar zenith angle (time of day)</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i data-feather="check-circle" class="text-cyan-400 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span>Wave conditions and sea state</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i data-feather="check-circle" class="text-cyan-400 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span>Presence of surface films or biological material</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <i data-feather="check-circle" class="text-cyan-400 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span>Atmospheric conditions and aerosol loading</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                                <img src="http://static.photos/science/1024x576/12" alt="Ocean Albedo Diagram" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-cyan-400/20 h-full">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why It Matters</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                                Ocean albedo oscillations play a crucial role in Earth's energy balance and climate system:
                            </p>
                            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
                                <div class="bg-gray-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <i data-feather="sun" class="text-yellow-400 mb-2"></i>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Energy Budget</h4>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Affects how much solar energy Earth retains</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-gray-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <i data-feather="thermometer" class="text-red-400 mb-2"></i>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Climate Feedback</h4>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Impacts temperature regulation patterns</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-gray-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <i data-feather="wind" class="text-blue-400 mb-2"></i>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Weather Patterns</h4>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Influences atmospheric circulation</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-gray-700/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                    <i data-feather="activity" class="text-green-400 mb-2"></i>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Ecosystems</h4>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Affects marine biological activity</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
